Package com.lambdaschool.foundation.models

Class CountryData

java.lang.Object
com.lambdaschool.foundation.models.CountryData
public class CountryData
extends java.lang.Object
The purpose of this model is to hold selective data from the rest country api system found at
https://restcountries.eu Note that this class is not an entity so will not get saved into the database.
